00:00:29.350 --> 00:00:33.140
Once word did get out, 100,000
people uprooted their lives

00:00:33.140 --> 00:00:34.925
and headed up to
the Klondike region,

00:00:34.925 --> 00:00:36.250
hoping to strike it rich.

00:00:36.250 --> 00:00:38.230
But it was a really
difficult journey,

00:00:38.230 --> 00:00:41.290
and only about 30,000
people actually made it.

00:00:41.290 --> 00:00:44.680
And of those, only a small
fraction, about 4,000 people,

00:00:44.680 --> 00:00:45.790
