discovered the gold first

00:01:31.625 --> 00:01:33.510
in Klondike are mixed, though.

00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:35.210
First, a friend
of Skookum's named

00:01:35.210 --> 00:01:37.250
George Carmack was
credited, because nobody

00:01:37.250 --> 00:01:38.490
would believe a native.

00:01:38.490 --> 00:01:41.100
But there are also accounts of
Kate Carmack, George's wife,

00:01:41.100 --> 00:01:43.797
