00:01:56.530 --> 00:01:58.690
They moved to Seattle
to enjoy their riches,

00:01:58.690 --> 00:02:01.148
but it was hard on both of
them, and they missed their home

00:02:01.148 --> 00:02:01.850
in in Dawson.

00:02:01.850 --> 00:02:04.980
Instead of allowing Kate to
come back north with him,

00:02:04.980 --> 00:02:07.835
