00:02:11.950 --> 00:02:13.465
And down in
California, Kate tried

00:02:13.465 --> 00:02:15.590
to make a legal appeal for
her share of the riches,

00:02:15.590 --> 00:02:17.541
but the court denied.

00:02:17.541 --> 00:02:19.540
George took all of their
money, and Kate went on

00:02:19.540 --> 00:02:23.100
to live off a government pension
in a cabin built by Skookum.

