to join the gold rush.

00:02:39.850 --> 00:02:41.760
The gold rush itself
wasn't kind to London.

00:02:41.760 --> 00:02:43.910
He became malnourished,
developed scurvy,

00:02:43.910 --> 00:02:45.890
and struggled with
serious health issues

00:02:45.890 --> 00:02:48.030
due to lack of food and shelter.

00:02:48.030 --> 00:02:49.890
But it's through these
hardships that Jack

00:02:49.890 --> 00:02:53.310
